snippet.title: PAW Patrol World - Announce Trailer
snippet.description: Paws up, is your family ready to attend the PAW Patrol Day Festival? 🐾🎊. Soon your child can join the Pups in PAW Patrol World 🎮, a new 3D adventure game where anything is PAWsible! Get ready to play, rescue and explore the world of PAW Patrol like never before. #PAWPatrol #PAWPatrolWorld
